Package: jj-starship
Version: @VERSION@
Section: vcs
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: Brian Cosgrove <brian@cosgrove.dev>
Depends: libc6, libgcc-s1, zlib1g
Homepage: https://github.com/dmmulroy/jj-starship
Description: Unified Git and Jujutsu Starship prompt module
 jj-starship provides a low-latency Starship custom module for Git and
 Jujutsu repositories.
 .
 This private package is built from upstream jj-starship sources and is not a
 Debian archive source package.
